   <body>
      <div class="SOTTO_PARA"><a name="DUCefd5b8282b38100582d7869cf45857d2"></a>Overhauling the front fork
      </div>
      <div class="SOTTO_PARA">
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e6859"> </a>It is advisable to loosen the top cap (7) when the fork leg is still fitted onto the motorcycle.
         </div>
      </div>
      <div class="SOTTO_PARA">
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e6862"> </a>The specific tools for the overhaul of the fork are described in Section, "<a href=".html#">Special tools for the frame </a>".
         </div>
      </div>
      <div class="SOTTO_PARA">
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e6868"> </a>Loosen the spring pre-load adjuster before unscrewing the plug (7).
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e6870"> </a>Unscrew the top plug (7) complete with the rebound damping adjuster.
         </div>
      </div>
      <div class="AggancioFigure">
         <center><img class="Default" src="img/DUC_MO_MTS1200_7_020503333.jpg"></center>
      </div>
      <div class="SOTTO_PARA">
         <div class="titoleto"><a name="d3e6875"> </a>Disassembling the front fork
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e6877"> </a>Restrain the lock nut (8) with a hex. wrench.
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e6879"> </a>Using another hexagon wrench, unscrew and remove the plug (7), with its sealing washer, from the cartridge (8).
         </div>
      </div>
      <div class="AggancioFigure">
         <center><img class="Default" src="img/DUC_MO_MTS1200_7_020603334.jpg"></center>
      </div>
      <div class="SOTTO_PARA">
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e6884"> </a>Unscrew the lock nut (8) up to the final threads on the cartridge (9).
         </div>
      </div>
      <div class="AggancioFigure">
         <center><img class="Default" src="img/DUC_MO_MTS1200_7_020703335.jpg"></center>
      </div>
      <div class="SOTTO_PARA">
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e6889"> </a>While holding the spring (10) with one hand, withdraw the bush (11) sideways and then slowly release spring (10).
         </div>
      </div>
      <div class="AggancioFigure">
         <center><img class="Default" src="img/DUC_MO_MTS1200_7_020803336.jpg"></center>
      </div>
      <div class="SOTTO_PARA">
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e6895"> </a>Slide off the spring (10).
         </div>
      </div>
      <div class="AggancioFigure">
         <center><img class="Default" src="img/DUC_MO_MTS1200_7_020903340.jpg"></center>
      </div>
      <div class="SOTTO_PARA">
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e6900"> </a>Slide the pre-load tube (12) and recover washer (13).
         </div>
      </div>
      <div class="AggancioFigure">
         <center><img class="Default" src="img/DUC_MO_MTS1200_7_021003337.jpg"></center>
      </div>
      <div class="AggancioFigure">
         <center><img class="Default" src="img/DUC_MO_MTS1200_7_021103338.jpg"></center>
      </div>
      <div class="SOTTO_PARA">
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e6907"> </a>Drain the oil from inside the leg by pumping with the outer sleeve (14) and the damper cartridge (9).
         </div>
      </div>
      <div class="AggancioFigure">
         <center><img class="Default" src="img/DUC_MO_MTS1200_7_021303339.jpg"></center>
      </div>
      <div class="Attenzione"><img class="Attenzione" width="28" height="25" style="display: inline; float: none; left: 0.0; text-align: left; top: 0.0;" src="img/warning.jpg">Warning
      </div>
      <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e6912"> </a>This movement generates pressure so that the oil will be rapidly expelled from the fork leg.
      </div>
      <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e6914"> </a>Aim the jet of oil into a previously prepared container and avoid contact with fork oil.
      </div>
      <div class="SOTTO_PARA">
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e6917"> </a>Block the slider (15) with a vice provided with protection jaws.
         </div>
      </div>
      <div class="AggancioFigure">
         <center><img class="Default" src="img/DUC_MO_MTS1200_7_021303347.jpg"></center>
      </div>
      <div class="SOTTO_PARA">
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e6922"> </a>Unscrew the compression damping adjuster (16).
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e6924"> </a>Remove the adjuster screw (16) and recover seal 13).
         </div>
      </div>
      <div class="AggancioFigure">
         <center><img class="Default" src="img/DUC_MO_MTS1200_7_021403348.jpg"></center>
      </div>
      <div class="SOTTO_PARA">
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e6930"> </a>Withdraw the cartridge assembly (9).
         </div>
      </div>
      <div class="AggancioFigure">
         <center><img class="Default" src="img/DUC_MO_MTS1200_7_021503349.jpg"></center>
      </div>
      <div class="SOTTO_PARA">
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e6935"> </a>Slip the dust seal (23) off the outer sleeve (18), prising it off with a screwdriver.
         </div>
      </div>
      <div class="AggancioFigure">
         <center><img class="Default" src="img/DUC_MO_MTS1200_7_021603350.jpg"></center>
      </div>
      <div class="SOTTO_PARA">
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e6940"> </a>Remove the snap ring (19).
         </div>
      </div>
      <div class="AggancioFigure">
         <center><img class="Default" src="img/DUC_MO_MTS1200_7_021703351.jpg"></center>
      </div>
      <div class="SOTTO_PARA">
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e6945"> </a>Take care not to damage the slider (15) and the seat of snap ring (19) in the outer sleeve (18).
         </div>
      </div>
      <div class="SOTTO_PARA">
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e6948"> </a>To separate the outer sleeve (18) from the slider (15), pull sharply outwards repeatedly to gradually displace the guide bushing
            (20).
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e6950"> </a>Insert the tip of a screwdriver in the slit in the bush (21) and open it up sufficiently to slide the bush off the slider.
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e6952"> </a>Remove the following parts from the slider:
         </div>
      </div>
      <div class="SOTTO_PARA">
         <div class="Trattino_outer" style="margin-left: 0pt;">
            <table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">
               <tr style="vertical-align: baseline;">
                  <td>
                     <div class="Trattino_inner" style="width: 20pt; white-space: nowrap;">- </div>
                  </td>
                  <td width="100%">
                     <div class="Trattino_inner">
                        <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e6956"> </a>upper bush (20);
                        </div>
                     </div>
                  </td>
               </tr>
            </table>
         </div>
         <div class="Trattino_outer" style="margin-left: 0pt;">
            <table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">
               <tr style="vertical-align: baseline;">
                  <td>
                     <div class="Trattino_inner" style="width: 20pt; white-space: nowrap;">- </div>
                  </td>
                  <td width="100%">
                     <div class="Trattino_inner">
                        <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e6959"> </a>collar (22);
                        </div>
                     </div>
                  </td>
               </tr>
            </table>
         </div>
         <div class="Trattino_outer" style="margin-left: 0pt;">
            <table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">
               <tr style="vertical-align: baseline;">
                  <td>
                     <div class="Trattino_inner" style="width: 20pt; white-space: nowrap;">- </div>
                  </td>
                  <td width="100%">
                     <div class="Trattino_inner">
                        <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e6962"> </a>sealing ring (24);
                        </div>
                     </div>
                  </td>
               </tr>
            </table>
         </div>
         <div class="Trattino_outer" style="margin-left: 0pt;">
            <table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">
               <tr style="vertical-align: baseline;">
                  <td>
                     <div class="Trattino_inner" style="width: 20pt; white-space: nowrap;">- </div>
                  </td>
                  <td width="100%">
                     <div class="Trattino_inner">
                        <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e6965"> </a>dust seal (23).
                        </div>
                     </div>
                  </td>
               </tr>
            </table>
         </div>
      </div>
      <div class="AggancioFigure">
         <center><img class="Default" src="img/DUC_MO_MTS1200_7_021803352.jpg"></center>
      </div>
      <div class="SOTTO_PARA">
         <div class="titoleto"><a name="d3e6971"> </a>Inspecting the front fork
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e6973"> </a>Place the spring on a flat surface and measure the free length (L).
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e6975"> </a>Service limit: 270&nbsp;mm.
         </div>
      </div>
      <div class="AggancioFigure">
         <center><img class="Default" src="img/DUC_MO_MTS1200_7_021903353.jpg"></center>
      </div>
      <div class="SOTTO_PARA">
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e6980"> </a>Replace the spring if the length is not within the specified limit.
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e6982"> </a>Inspect the outer surfaces of both sliders and the internal surfaces of both sleeves. They must be free from scoring, steps,
            or dents.
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e6984"> </a>Check that the stanchions are straight: maximum allowed error 0.10 mm.
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e6986"> </a>Whenever the slider is removed from the sleeve it is good practice to replace bushes (21) and (20).
         </div>
      </div>
      <div class="AggancioFigure">
         <center><img class="Default" src="img/DUC_MO_MTS1200_7_022003354.jpg"></center>
      </div>
      <div class="SOTTO_PARA">
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e6991"> </a>Check the collar (22) for distortion in the area indicated. Replace if distorted.
         </div>
      </div>
      <div class="AggancioFigure">
         <center><img class="Default" src="img/DUC_MO_MTS1200_7_022103356.jpg"></center>
      </div>
      <div class="SOTTO_PARA">
         <div class="titoleto"><a name="d3e6996"> </a>Reassembling the front fork
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e6998"> </a>Clamp slider in a vice.
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e7000"> </a>Protect the end of the slider with tape.
         </div>
      </div>
      <div class="SOTTO_PARA">
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e7003"> </a>Before installation, smear the sliding edges of sealing ring (24) with fork oil or seal grease.
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e7005"> </a>Install the seal (24) with the marked surface facing the dust seal (230).
         </div>
      </div>
      <div class="SOTTO_PARA">
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e7008"> </a>Install the following components in slider (15):
         </div>
      </div>
      <div class="SOTTO_PARA">
         <div class="Trattino_outer" style="margin-left: 0pt;">
            <table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">
               <tr style="vertical-align: baseline;">
                  <td>
                     <div class="Trattino_inner" style="width: 20pt; white-space: nowrap;">- </div>
                  </td>
                  <td width="100%">
                     <div class="Trattino_inner">
                        <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e7012"> </a>dust seal (23);
                        </div>
                     </div>
                  </td>
               </tr>
            </table>
         </div>
         <div class="Trattino_outer" style="margin-left: 0pt;">
            <table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">
               <tr style="vertical-align: baseline;">
                  <td>
                     <div class="Trattino_inner" style="width: 20pt; white-space: nowrap;">- </div>
                  </td>
                  <td width="100%">
                     <div class="Trattino_inner">
                        <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e7015"> </a>snap ring (19);
                        </div>
                     </div>
                  </td>
               </tr>
            </table>
         </div>
         <div class="Trattino_outer" style="margin-left: 0pt;">
            <table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">
